#MongoDB - Database

- install database
http://docs.mongodb.org/master/installation/

#Node - Linguage

- install NODEJS
 https://nodejs.org/en/download/
 https://github.com/nodejs/node-v0.x-archive/wiki/Installing-Node.js-via-package-manager?utm_source=%5Bdeliciuos%5D&utm_medium=twitter

#NPM - package manager

- install NPM
https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-use-npm-to-manage-node-js-packages-on-a-linux-server
https://docs.npmjs.com/cli/install

------------------------------------------------

#ENVORIMENT

***Init Database***

> mongorestore /opt/collector/db_init/

***Install Package***
> cd collector

# application configuration - Administration 
> cd admin
> npm install
> pm2 start bin/www
- open in browser IP:3000



***Rum background application ***
> node twitter_get_info_user.js & node twitter_get_tweets.js

